texts.text: 57Digital is a mobile application development company based in Sheffield, England. It is run by Jamie Chapman and Luke Dixon, two software engineers from Sheffield.
57Digital is responsible for creating an official[1] Minecraft companion guide, Minecraft Explorer.

Minecraft Explorer Pro
Minecraft Skin Studio
Minecraft Papercraft Studio
Minecraft Skin Scanner
Seeds Explorer - Minecraft Edition
"Need a companion app for Minecraft? We recommend this one: http://itunes.apple.com/ng/app/minecraft-explorer-pro/id449354665?mt=8 …" – @carlmanneh on Twitter, March 21, 2012
